This paper deals with natural language processing and neural networks, which are typically covered under the arXiv category of Computer Science - Computation and Language (cs.CL). The use of memory augmented neural networks and meta-learning also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the reduction of errors and the optimization of resources, which could fall under the categories of neural networks (cs.NE) and systems and control (cs.SY).
